oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Moultrie-Douglas County Fair (July 17) (16676)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fairs; Overstreet, Tommy; Trask, Diana; Hall, Tom T.;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing the Moultrie-Douglas County Fair schedule with Tommy Overstreet and O. B. McClinton on July 17, Dr. Bop and the Headliners on July 18, Diana Trask on July 19, and Tom T. Hall on July 20. Poster was ordered by Mid West Promotions (purchase order 16676). For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32362.
